Uses of Interface
interfaces.IKeyword

  • Packages that use IKeyword 
    Package Description
    actionKeywords
    actionKeywords package contains all concrete classes for Action Keywords that implement the IKeyword interface and extend the ActionKeyword abstract class
    assertKeywords
    assertKeywords package contains all concrete classes for Assert Keywords that implement the IKeyword interface and extend the AssertKeyword abstract class
    framework
    This package contains all base Framework classes
    getKeywords
    getKeywords package contains all concrete classes for Get Keywords that implement the IKeyword interface and extend the GetKeyword abstract class
    interfaces
    public interfaces for defining the model of how the framework works with keywords, logging, and Excel workbooks.
    logging
    This package contains classes for implementing logging in the framework.
    touchKeywords
    touchKeywords package contains all concrete classes for Touch Action Keywords that implement the IKeyword interface and extend the TouchKeyword abstract class
    waitKeywords
    waitKeywords package contains all concrete classes for Wait Keywords that implement the IKeyword interface and extend the WaitKeyword abstract class
